dataset.title: Hymenasplenium hovenkampii (Aspleniaceae), a new bipinnatisect fern species from Lesser Sunda Islands of Indonesia

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Xu, Ke-Wang, Liu, Yu-Xuan, Chen, Yi-Fei, Zhang, Li-Bing (2023): Hymenasplenium hovenkampii (Aspleniaceae), a new bipinnatisect fern species from Lesser Sunda Islands of Indonesia.
